Below is the data preprocessing stage where it includes¶

i)Lowercase ii)Tokenization iii)Removing the special character iv)Removing the special words and punctuation v)Stemming

In [54]:
#Data preprocessing
def transform_text(text):
    text=text.lower()
    text=nltk.word_tokenize(text)
    y=[]
    for i in text:
        if i.isalnum():
            y.append(i)
    text=y[:]
    y.clear()
    for i in text:
        if i not in stopwords.words('english') and i not in string.punctuation:
            y.append(i)
    text=y[:]
    y.clear()
    for i in text:
        y.append(ps.stem(i))
    return " ".join(y)
